00:05:05.480 --> 00:05:06.750
Expel it?

00:05:08.110 --> 00:05:10.680
And go back to being
that lowly little spider?

00:05:11.950 --> 00:05:14.610
The spider that could
only crouch in the corner,

00:05:14.750 --> 00:05:16.920
praying for you to look my way?

00:05:19.360 --> 00:05:20.000
No.

00:05:21.160 --> 00:05:22.680
I'd rather die.

00:05:24.920 --> 00:05:26.360
This is a silence talisman.

00:05:26.360 --> 00:05:27.070
Qingcheng.

00:05:27.680 --> 00:05:29.080
Don't make a sound later.

00:05:30.390 --> 00:05:31.600
Just listen.

00:05:31.800 --> 00:05:33.130
What are you going to do?

00:05:34.180 --> 00:05:34.950
Qingcheng?

00:05:35.190 --> 00:05:36.040
Either way...

00:05:37.190 --> 00:05:38.870
I've lost you.

00:05:39.830 --> 00:05:40.800
