00:06:52.070 --> 00:06:53.310
or I do!

00:06:59.310 --> 00:07:00.440
Young Master Fugui.

00:07:09.680 --> 00:07:10.560
Qingcheng,

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:11.690
let me out.

00:07:18.560 --> 00:07:19.360
Black Fox,

00:07:20.270 --> 00:07:21.070
come out!

00:07:26.720 --> 00:07:28.360
It hurts! It hurts so much!

00:07:28.510 --> 00:07:29.250
Sister!

00:07:29.390 --> 00:07:30.430
Help me, Sister!

00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:31.920
Young Master Fugui,

00:07:31.920 --> 00:07:32.800
stop.

00:07:37.750 --> 00:07:38.950
I'll say it one more time:

00:07:38.950 --> 00:07:39.630
Black Fox,

00:07:39.630 --> 00:07:40.620
get the hell out!

00:07:45.600 --> 00:07:46.190
Sister,

00:07:46.510 --> 00:07:47.800
are you going to leave me

00:07:47.800 --> 00:07:48.630
and give up on me?

00:07:48.630 --> 00:07:49.510
Sister!

00:07:58.040 --> 00:07:59.600
Never!

00:08:20.510 --> 00:08:21.920
Right now, the priority is

00:08:21.920 --> 00:08:23.070
to figure out

00:08:23.480 --> 00:08:25.430
how to expel the Black Fox
from Qingcheng's body.

00:08:25.430 --> 00:08:26.750
Wangquan Fugui,

00:08:27.160 --> 00:08:28.960
it was I who knocked Qingtong out

00:08:29.310 --> 00:08:30.480
and took her away.

00:08:30.480 --> 00:08:31.750
It was I

00:08:31.750 --> 00:08:34.409
who tried every way
to stop her from finding you.

00:08:34.909 --> 00:08:37.080
It was I who told her you were dead

00:08:37.320 --> 00:08:39.360
to make her let go of you.

00:08:39.960 --> 00:08:42.240
I did all of that!

00:08:54.390 --> 00:08:56.030
Wangquan Fugui,

00:08:56.150 --> 00:08:57.240
that's it.

00:08:57.790 --> 00:08:58.960
Hit me.

00:08:59.360 --> 00:09:01.270
The crueler, the better.

00:09:12.910 --> 00:09:15.710
If Qingcheng keeps provoking
Young Master Fugui,

00:09:15.790 --> 00:09:17.720
he'll die along with the Black Fox.

00:09:21.250 --> 00:09:23.510
The one who deserves to die
is the Black Fox.

00:09:23.510 --> 00:09:25.120
I can't abandon Qingcheng.

00:09:29.960 --> 00:09:30.620
Qingcheng,

00:09:31.270 --> 00:09:32.910
you've colluded with the Black Fox,

00:09:32.910 --> 00:09:34.510
striking cruelly at humans.

00:09:34.910 --> 00:09:37.440
You even dragged Qingtong
into your schemes.

00:09:37.550 --> 00:09:38.680
Come back with me now

00:09:39.120 --> 00:09:41.980
and confess everything about you
and the Black Fox.

00:09:48.600 --> 00:09:49.730
Young Master Fugui.

00:09:50.200 --> 00:09:52.240
Qingcheng was simply bewitched
by the Black Fox.

00:09:52.240 --> 00:09:53.510
Please spare his life!

00:09:55.390 --> 00:09:56.080
Qingtong.

00:09:57.150 --> 00:09:58.750
I never intended to kill him.

00:09:58.750 --> 00:10:01.480
I only wanted to expel
the Black Fox from his body.

00:10:02.790 --> 00:10:03.920
But if you do that...

00:10:04.790 --> 00:10:06.120
Qingcheng will die too.

00:10:06.870 --> 00:10:08.600
In order to expel the Black Fox,

00:10:09.150 --> 00:10:11.200
he'd even sacrifice himself.

00:10:11.790 --> 00:10:13.270
Do you think he'd spare me?

00:10:13.270 --> 00:10:14.000
Shut up!

00:10:14.550 --> 00:10:16.510
All disciples of the alliance, listen up!

00:10:16.510 --> 00:10:17.320
Search this place thoroughly,

00:10:17.320 --> 00:10:18.670
inside and out!

00:10:18.940 --> 00:10:20.360
If you find any suspicious demons,

00:10:20.360 --> 00:10:22.080
bring them back to
Wangquan Manor immediately!

00:10:22.080 --> 00:10:22.960
-Yes, sir!
-Yes, sir!

00:10:22.960 --> 00:10:23.550
Sister,

00:10:24.150 --> 00:10:26.080
